Title: No One Can Hear You
Writer: Pendleton Ward (creator), Ako Castuera, Jesse Moynihan, Mark Banker (story), Kent Osborne (story), Pendleton Ward (story), Patrick McHale (story)
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Hynden Walch, Tom Kenny
Plot: After trying to stop a deer that has been licking the Candy Kingdom people, Finn wakes up in a hospital to find everyone missing expect Jake who is acting very strange.
